`,(0,n.jsxs)(e.p,{children:["The error message is a bit intriguing, though. It seems that the ",(0,n.jsx)(e.code,{children:"async"})," keyword makes our function return a ",(0,n.jsx)(e.code,{children:"Future"})," instead of the declared type."]}),`
